== A compositional example: Good Morning Sincity

In this composition, polyrhythms consisting of mirrored pairs of swinging meters morph smoothly from section to section: 

($7/8$ / $11/8$) $arrow$ ($11/8$ / $4/4)$ $arrow$ ($4/4$ / $12/8$) $arrow$ ($3/2$ / $9/8$) $arrow$ ($9/8$ / $15/8$) $arrow$ ($15/8$ / $5/4$) $arrow$ ($5/8$ / $7/8)$

